metadata.name: Symbiote - Shield
metadata.description:
Symbiotes act as the main form of energy in the surreal planet. 

Everything has a price, and that price is paid by acquiring a symbiote. 

Every person needs to have 3 symbiotes which are "Shield", "Heal" and "Damage" in order to step inside the realms of the cyberworld.

More to follow soon


Details:  3840x2160
